 for the\nexperiments were gathered using a Muse EEG headband with four electrodes\ncorresponding to TP9, AF7, AF8, and TP10 locations of the international EEG\nplacement standard. The EEG MindBigData digits dataset was gathered from the\nTP9, FP1, FP2, and TP10 locations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2019 16:49:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-11"}
