t the weakening of Haj\\'{o}s' conjecture is true\nfor graphs of bounded treewidth in a stronger sense; the final result is the\nfirst $O(s)$ bound on the clustered chromatic number of graphs with no\n$K_{s+1}$-subdivision.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Aug 2019 06:36:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 00:28:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2020 02:22:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 03:31:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-28"}
